    <title id="GUID-91564DD8-F89B-4955-AEF0-22036F141C99">Figure element</title>

    <shortdesc>The figure (&lt;fig&gt;) element is a display context (sometimes called an "exhibit") with an
        optional title for a wide variety of content.
    </shortdesc>

